614
00:36:35,970 --> 00:36:36,710
Never mind.

615
00:36:38,430 --> 00:36:39,360
Miss Yu,

616
00:36:39,750 --> 00:36:40,880
I can see from your face

617
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:41,870
that something did happen.

618
00:36:42,640 --> 00:36:43,830
Tell me what it is.

619
00:36:46,310 --> 00:36:47,710
Someone from Xiuli Army came,

620
00:36:47,860 --> 00:36:48,890
asking to see you.

621
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:50,400
I stopped him.

622
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:53,360
Someone from Xiuli Army?

623
00:36:55,110 --> 00:36:56,450
His name is Ge Qi.

624
00:36:56,930 --> 00:36:57,840
He asked

625
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,410
if you remembered a warrant

626
00:36:59,410 --> 00:37:00,140
granted by Yuwen Yue

627
00:37:00,140 --> 00:37:01,100
with which you could get new bows

628
00:37:01,100 --> 00:37:02,130
for Xiuli Army from the arsenal.

629
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:03,690
I remember.

630
00:37:03,910 --> 00:37:05,240
I gave it to He Xiao.

631
00:37:05,780 --> 00:37:07,400
What? Did he not get them?

632
00:37:08,830 --> 00:37:09,750
He said

633
00:37:09,750 --> 00:37:11,200
He Xiao lost that warrant.

634
00:37:11,470 --> 00:37:13,120
But people in the arsenal said

635
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:14,360
they received the warrant

636
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:15,570
and they gave the bows and arrows

637
00:37:15,570 --> 00:37:16,840
to Xiuli Army.

638
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:20,120
However, no such weapons

639
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:21,710
can be found in Xiuli Army.

640
00:37:22,160 --> 00:37:24,210
Now, He Xiao is arrested

641
00:37:24,500 --> 00:37:26,300
and accused of embezzling weapons.

642
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:27,630
He is to be executed.

643
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,970
Executed? When?

644
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:33,280
At noon today.

645
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:36,070
At noon today?

646
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,770
I’ll go and check it.

647
00:37:46,300 --> 00:37:48,500
He Xiao, time is running out.

648
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:50,160
Are you going to confess or not?

649
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:53,080
I have nothing to confess.

650
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:55,210
I lost the warrant.

651
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:57,070
I should take the blame for that.

652
00:37:57,880 --> 00:37:59,360
However, Commander!

653
00:37:59,650 --> 00:38:02,580
You accuse me of embezzling soldiers’ pay

654
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:04,320
and reselling military weapons.

655
00:38:05,540 --> 00:38:06,420
I will never

656
00:38:07,640 --> 00:38:08,620
plead guilty.

657
00:38:11,450 --> 00:38:12,690
You sound stubborn!

658
00:38:13,510 --> 00:38:16,280
Fine. Since you don’t confess to me,

659
00:38:16,650 --> 00:38:18,370
confess to the demons

660
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,150
in the hell.

661
00:38:21,650 --> 00:38:23,120
He Xiao embezzled soldiers’ pay

662
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:24,260
and resold military weapons.

663
00:38:24,490 --> 00:38:27,000
According to military laws,
he should be executed!

664
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:28,180
Commander!

665
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:29,980
Neither Chief Commander
nor Deputy Commander is here.

666
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:30,840
How can you decide alone

667
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,330
such an important issue?

668
00:38:32,850 --> 00:38:35,080
Mr. He has been in the army for years.

669
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:38,030
He is conscientious and loving!

670
00:38:38,550 --> 00:38:39,820
He came to Chang’an

671
00:38:40,230 --> 00:38:41,600
with no family around!

672
00:38:41,960 --> 00:38:43,170
What does he need money for?

673
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:44,720
Yeah.

674
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:46,540
He is a good man!

675
00:38:46,540 --> 00:38:47,930
Don’t kill the innocent man!

676
00:38:47,930 --> 00:38:49,730
Don’t kill the innocent man!

677
00:38:49,730 --> 00:38:52,880
- Don’t kill the innocent man!
- Shut up!

678
00:38:53,140 --> 00:38:55,120
The evidence for his sin is conclusive.

679
00:38:55,380 --> 00:38:56,930
As the commander of Xiuli Army,

680
00:38:57,270 --> 00:38:58,760
I have the authority to punish him.

681
00:38:59,030 --> 00:39:00,920
But you plead for him.

682
00:39:01,570 --> 00:39:03,460
Are you his confederates?

683
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:04,300
Commander Xue.

684
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:05,670
Don’t sling mud at us!

685
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:06,770
Don’t sling mud at us!

686
00:39:06,770 --> 00:39:07,680
Don’t sling mud at us!

687
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:09,230
- Don’t sling mud at us!
- Shut up!

688
00:39:09,230 --> 00:39:10,560
Don’t sling mud at us!

689
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:11,790
There is human testimony
and material evidence.

690
00:39:12,770 --> 00:39:14,730
I won’t take the blame

691
00:39:15,010 --> 00:39:16,920
for slinging mud at you!

692
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:18,320
But look at you!

693
00:39:18,950 --> 00:39:21,570
You slandered your superior.

694
00:39:21,830 --> 00:39:23,190
What punishment do you think you deserve?

695
00:39:23,190 --> 00:39:23,820
Our Vice Commander

696
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:24,580
isn’t a corrupt man.

697
00:39:24,580 --> 00:39:25,590
Let him go!

698
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:27,180
Let him go!

699
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:27,980
Let him go!

700
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:29,100
- Let him go!
- Shut up!

701
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:30,230
Let him go!

702
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:31,970
Are you going to rebel?

703
00:39:31,970 --> 00:39:33,850
Let him go!

704
00:39:33,850 --> 00:39:35,410
Let him go!

705
00:39:35,410 --> 00:39:36,560
Dudes!

706
00:39:37,260 --> 00:39:39,120
Let him go!

707
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:40,930
Let him go!

708
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:44,610
Dudes.

709
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,330
I appreciate

710
00:39:48,170 --> 00:39:49,660
your help.

711
00:39:51,260 --> 00:39:52,110
However,

712
00:39:53,420 --> 00:39:55,460
I took you to Chang’an,

713
00:39:55,460 --> 00:39:56,640
leaving our hometown behind

714
00:39:56,810 --> 00:39:58,250
and struggled for life,

715
00:39:59,060 --> 00:40:00,250
not because I wanted you

716
00:40:00,250 --> 00:40:01,710
to get killed like this.

717
00:40:02,380 --> 00:40:03,970
We can’t go home

718
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,850
or acknowledge our families.

719
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:08,280
Everyone hates us.

720
00:40:08,830 --> 00:40:10,330
We’re even abandoned by the whole world,

721
00:40:12,610 --> 00:40:13,900
only because

722
00:40:13,900 --> 00:40:15,270
we’re known as traitors!

723
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,200
But I know

724
00:40:18,660 --> 00:40:19,880
you are not.

725
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,610
Nor am I!

726
00:40:25,330 --> 00:40:26,800
Who can tell me

727
00:40:27,470 --> 00:40:28,580
the highest honor

728
00:40:28,580 --> 00:40:30,400
for a soldier?

729
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:33,820
Die in the battlefield!

730
00:40:35,190 --> 00:40:38,710
Dudes, I don’t think

731
00:40:39,850 --> 00:40:41,600
I’ve got a chance
to die in the battlefield.

732
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:43,920
Therefore,

733
00:40:45,550 --> 00:40:46,930
you must survive.

734
00:40:47,740 --> 00:40:50,310
When you have a chance
to protect your country,

735
00:40:50,310 --> 00:40:51,670
and fight in the battlefield,

736
00:40:51,820 --> 00:40:53,790
kill more enemies for me!

737
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:56,880
Use your blood

738
00:40:58,110 --> 00:40:59,780
to wash off the shame

739
00:40:59,780 --> 00:41:01,240
we’ve carried!

740
00:41:04,220 --> 00:41:06,270
When I saw that in heaven,

741
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:10,990
I would be grateful!

742
00:41:13,420 --> 00:41:14,760
Cut the crap.

743
00:41:14,920 --> 00:41:17,350
Time is out. Kill him.

744
00:41:17,970 --> 00:41:19,220
You can’t kill him!

745
00:41:19,220 --> 00:41:19,960
What are you doing?

746
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,850
You can’t kill him!

747
00:41:20,850 --> 00:41:21,760
Time is out!

748
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:23,530
You can’t kill him!

749
00:41:26,070 --> 00:41:26,890
Stop!

750
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:30,580
Stop!

751
00:41:35,030 --> 00:41:36,050
Ms. Chu?

752
00:41:36,870 --> 00:41:38,260
What are you coming for?

753
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:42,170
What are you doing, Commander?

754
00:41:42,410 --> 00:41:45,100
Punishing a sinner
according to military laws.

755
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,940
What is He Xiao’s sin?

756
00:41:48,090 --> 00:41:50,440
He embezzled soldiers’ pay
and resold military weapons.

757
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:51,860
Which pay?

758
00:41:52,160 --> 00:41:53,780
Bows and arrows

759
00:41:53,780 --> 00:41:54,480
General Yuwen granted us.

760
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,930
He Xiao said he lost the warrant

761
00:41:57,930 --> 00:41:59,380
and couldn’t take them back.

762
00:41:59,810 --> 00:42:01,460
But according to the arsenal,

763
00:42:01,460 --> 00:42:02,260
they received the warrant

764
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:03,440
and delivered the weapons.

765
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,940
If he hadn’t stolen them,

766
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:06,350
who else could have done that?

767
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:08,940
Maybe someone got the weapons

768
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,060
in his name?

769
00:42:10,060 --> 00:42:11,360
I don’t know that.

770
00:42:11,740 --> 00:42:12,910
Even so,

771
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:14,750
he is to blame for dropping the warrant

772
00:42:14,750 --> 00:42:16,580
and making the weapons gone!

773
00:42:16,730 --> 00:42:18,190
He should be killed as well!

774
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,400
Fine, do it then.

775
00:42:30,240 --> 00:42:31,170
Ms. Chu.

776
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,570
What do you mean?

777
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:35,250
General Yuwen gave the warrant to me.

778
00:42:35,370 --> 00:42:36,470
I lost it.

779
00:42:36,770 --> 00:42:37,940
It didn’t concern He Xiao.

780
00:42:37,940 --> 00:42:39,150
He was just taking the blame for me.

781
00:42:39,340 --> 00:42:40,280
Ms. Chu.

782
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:40,910
Say no more.

783
00:42:41,910 --> 00:42:43,360
I am on a mission given by His Majesty.

784
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:44,750
Also, I am a military officer.

785
00:42:45,270 --> 00:42:46,490
The warrant was given to me.

786
00:42:46,490 --> 00:42:47,440
I should take the blame

787
00:42:47,660 --> 00:42:49,190
for its loss.

788
00:42:49,930 --> 00:42:53,010
Ms. Chu, you asked

789
00:42:53,010 --> 00:42:54,340
to get involved.

790
00:42:55,510 --> 00:42:57,750
Do you think

791
00:42:57,750 --> 00:42:58,600
I don’t dare to kill you?

792
00:43:00,730 --> 00:43:01,910
You certainly dare.

793
00:43:02,750 --> 00:43:04,130
As the Commander,

794
00:43:04,130 --> 00:43:05,310
you dare to kill anyone.

795
00:43:06,070 --> 00:43:06,750
However,

796
00:43:06,750 --> 00:43:07,810
let me remind you.

797
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:10,170
When the Crown Prince Xiao Ce
was assassinated,

798
00:43:10,170 --> 00:43:11,640
I stayed with him

799
00:43:11,910 --> 00:43:13,260
and protected him.

800
00:43:13,530 --> 00:43:14,150
The Crown Prince Xiao Ce

801
00:43:14,150 --> 00:43:15,630
pleaded to His Majesty on my behalf.

802
00:43:16,020 --> 00:43:18,020
His Majesty allowed me
to get recovered first

803
00:43:18,260 --> 00:43:19,910
before he rewarded me later.

804
00:43:19,910 --> 00:43:21,280
If you want to kill me,

805
00:43:21,500 --> 00:43:23,360
you’d better report to your superior,

806
00:43:24,110 --> 00:43:25,650
in case you get into trouble

807
00:43:25,650 --> 00:43:27,360
due to your own decision.

808
00:43:28,550 --> 00:43:29,440
Commander Xue.

809
00:43:29,970 --> 00:43:31,610
I’m saying it for your own good.

810
00:43:34,420 --> 00:43:37,230
Fine, I’m going to report it.

811
00:43:38,130 --> 00:43:39,590
I’d like to see

812
00:43:40,400 --> 00:43:42,620
how much support you can have!

813
00:43:43,070 --> 00:43:44,880
You two, stay on your knees!

814
00:43:45,250 --> 00:43:46,650
See you, Commander Xue.

